THIS REPOSITORY IS FOR CONFIGURATION AND RELATED FILES LIKE .bashrc OR
MOZILLA bookmarks.html

The scripts assume the existence of ~/local/scripts.  Ad hoc as heck,
huh?

scripts/its-all-text-emacs.sh
  for the It's All Text firefox plugin.  After installing the plugin
  set the editor preference to point to
  local/scripts/its-all-text-emacs.sh

